---
title: Beef, Sweet Potato & Black Bean Tostadas with Bell Pepper, Salsa & Creamy Guacamole
description: If you can’t decide between the flavors of your fave taco and the satisfying crunch-factor of a plate of nachos, you’ll love tostadas—the perfect marriage of the two. These vegan masterpieces are piled high with hearty refried beans, roasted veggies seasoned with our amazing fajita spice blend, fresh tomato salsa, and rich and creamy guac–so tasty you won’t miss the meat! If you’re looking for the ideal meal to get you ready for summer living, this one will have you eating fresh and fast, with more time to enjoy fun in the sun!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/vegan-sweet-potato-black-bean-tostadas-fc925418.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/6489e2f40b7af205da01ba40.pdf
